{"tid":1949323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"慕容公子新片又幾好睇","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T10:51:38.000Z","uid":227275,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49c47840c8a5bc492db4869abfe66cfd102580fe","tid":1949323,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQM0I8TtX2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMQM0I8TtX2A&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=d4e9c53c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQM0I8TtX2A</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係講得幾好 但勵志故事主角佢完全稱唔上 仲改左新名叫勵志子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過打擊傳銷狗 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好過臭雞姐又偷人野又呃人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043af8ddacef97ac711416fa41359e7d0a9d503a","tid":1949323,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33ed78242fbf32707db8f9f15713f3d74ba4080","tid":1949323,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c4bb42a2f16072c1653d2b4dd5a4c25b8d1771cc","tid":1949323,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"WHO?"},{"pid":"d963b06858263fbd912780d5446f287af00848ce","tid":1949323,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4bb42a2f16072c1653d2b4dd5a4c25b8d1771cc","tid":1949323,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"WHO?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7683d81b76b437293cd34734287a2a7e2d4c5807","tid":1949323,"uid":56999,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"你條傻仔成日改名上連登拉view<br />\n<br />\n煩唔能煩"},{"pid":"f13d9aaa97347dab2065892efb829e09962f8c16","tid":1949323,"uid":214300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"幾好教下啲小學雞同中學雞，佢地宜家係屋企打機打得咁爽大個就真係打飛機"},{"pid":"c255314e49a92e0b3a96687a8d44576b9aa66ea8","tid":1949323,"uid":215700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"前半部分講得幾好嘅<br />\n後半部分講佢自己好學真係笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連小學英文程度都無 真係好難稱得上好學 <br />\n不過佢好似搬左去台灣 如果成世台灣住又真係唔駛用到英文嘅"},{"pid":"359704f710bfc4f6a324284acb079fbe392bb54e","tid":1949323,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7683d81b76b437293cd34734287a2a7e2d4c5807","tid":1949323,"uid":56999,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"你條傻仔成日改名上連登拉view<br />\n<br />\n煩唔能煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4e2b202344ca520073f6b869366368e486cb45","tid":1949323,"uid":323051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:52:39.000Z","msg":"一個叫人唔讀書嘅叫人讀書<br />\n啲嘢係啱 但由佢把口講出唔可信喎<br />\n想洗底既 至少捐哂佢靠中學雞賺既錢比手足先<br />\n香港唔需要一個香港人係到革命 但佢係台灣食女玩既kol<br />\n你諗清楚佢呢個人值唔值得信同係香港有市場<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4JWF501sPc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4JWF501sPc0&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=2235f1a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4JWF501sPc0</a><br />\nBob叔個時屌醒佢 仲話人偷換概念<br />\n柒左 被人圍屌先過台灣<br />\n算啦 仲想返黎香港市場 証明做返真。香港人<br />\n我撐返佢又點話 總之宜家比個dislike 先<br />\n同eminleo 一樣出返黎 借疫情 想上位 立心不良"},{"pid":"111b7f5af463e6303714039150d79eaab500a482","tid":1949323,"uid":140852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7683d81b76b437293cd3473428